data.description: Come and check out this spacious 4 bedroom home located in a fantastic neighborhood! Beautiful foyer with hard wood floors and formal dining area along with a spacious kitchen that is open to an informal dining space and family room which flows into the living/great room. The laundry is conveniently located on the main floor as well as a recently updated bathroom. Upstairs, the large primary bedroom boats its own bath! Outside, enjoy the large deck and yard. Perfect for entertaining or relaxing.
